		<title>米其林餐盤主廚監製　MUMU推出創新潔淨無添加寶寶燉飯</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/11/06/%e7%b1%b3%e5%85%b6%e6%9e%97%e9%a4%90%e7%9b%a4%e4%b8%bb%e5%bb%9a%e7%9b%a3%e8%a3%bd%e3%80%80mumu%e6%8e%a8%e5%87%ba%e5%89%b5%e6%96%b0%e6%bd%94%e6%b7%a8%e7%84%a1%e6%b7%bb%e5%8a%a0%e5%af%b6%e5%af%b6/</link>
		
